### Require administrator privileges ###
RequireAdmin

### Privacy Tweaks ###
# DisableTelemetry
DisableWiFiSense
DisableSmartScreen
DisableWebSearch
DisableAppSuggestions
DisableTailoredExperiences
SetP2PUpdateInternet
DisableDiagTrack
EnableCortanaRequisites

### Security Tweaks ###
SetUACLow
DisableAdminShares
SetCurrentNetworkPrivate
DisableDefender
SetDEPOptOut
EnableDotNetStrongCrypto

### Service Tweaks ###
DisableUpdateDriver
DisableUpdateRestart
DisableHomeGroups
DisableRemoteAssistance
EnableRemoteDesktop
EnableRemoteDesktopNLA
DisableAutoplay
DisableAutorun
EnableStorageSense
SetBIOSTimeUTC

### UI Tweaks ###
HideAccountProtectionWarn
DisableStickyKeys
ShowTaskManagerDetails
ShowFileOperationsDetails
EnableFileDeleteConfirm
HideTaskbarSearch
HideTaskView
ShowSmallTaskbarIcons
SetTaskbarCombineNever
HideTaskbarPeopleIcon
HideRecentlyAddedApps
SetControlPanelSmallIcons

